cat << EOF
Soya 3D is a high level 3D engine for Python ; it aims at being to 3D what
Python is to programming : easy and powerfull. It is designed with games in
mind, focusing both on performance and ease-of-use. It relies on OpenGL, SDL
and Cal3D.

Features includes :

    * portals
    * terrain rendering (heighmap)
    * characters animations with Cal3D
    * Blender exporter
    * tutorials set
    * ... 
EOF
